{"lemma":"شَرِكَ","slug":"شَرِكَ","root":"ش.ر.ك","root_slug":"ش-ر-ك","root_link":"/words/roots/ش-ر-ك","pos":"V","pos_camel":"verb","paradigm":[{"role":"past_2ms","form":"شَرِكْتَ","in_corpus":false,"count":null,"asp":"p","per":"2","gen":"m","num":"s"},{"role":"past_2fs","form":"شَرِكْتِ","in_corpus":false,"count":null,"asp":"p","per":"2","gen":"f","num":"s"},{"role":"past_2md","form":"شَرِكْتُما","in_corpus":false,"count":null,"asp":"p","per":"2","gen":"m","num":"d"},{"role":"past_2mp","form":"شَرِكْتُم","in_corpus":false,"count":null,"asp":"p","per":"2","gen":"m","num":"p"},{"role":"past_2fp","form":"شَرِكْتُنَّ","in_corpus":false,"count":null,"asp":"p","per":"2","gen":"f","num":"p"},{"role":"past_3ms","form":"شَرِكَ","in_corpus":true,"count":11,"asp":"p","per":"3","gen":"m","num":"s"},{"role":"past_3fs","form":"شَرِكَت","in_corpus":false,"count":null,"asp":"p","per":"3","gen":"f","num":"s"},{"role":"past_3md","form":"شَرِكا","in_corpus":true,"count":4,"asp":"p","per":"3","gen":"m","num":"d"},{"role":"past_3fd","form":"شَرِكَتا","in_corpus":false,"count":null,"asp":"p","per":"3","gen":"f","num":"d"},{"role":"past_3mp","form":"شَرِكُوا","in_corpus":true,"count":1,"asp":"p","per":"3","gen":"m","num":"p"},{"role":"past_3fp","form":"شَرِكْنَ","in_corpus":false,"count":null,"asp":"p","per":"3","gen":"f","num":"p"},{"role":"present_2ms","form":"تَشْرَك","in_corpus":true,"count":8,"asp":"i","per":"2","gen":"m","num":"s"},{"role":"present_2fs","form":"تَشْرَكِينَ","in_corpus":false,"count":null,"asp":"i","per":"2","gen":"f","num":"s"},{"role":"present_2fs","form":"تَشْرَكِي","in_corpus":false,"count":null,"asp":"i","per":"2","gen":"f","num":"s"},{"role":"present_2md","form":"تَشْرَكانِ","in_corpus":false,"count":null,"asp":"i","per":"2","gen":"m","num":"d"},{"role":"present_2md","form":"تَشْرَكا","in_corpus":false,"count":null,"asp":"i","per":"2","gen":"m","num":"d"},{"role":"present_2mp","form":"تَشْرَكُونَ","in_corpus":true,"count":1,"asp":"i","per":"2","gen":"m","num":"p"},{"role":"present_2mp","form":"تَشْرَكُوا","in_corpus":true,"count":2,"asp":"i","per":"2","gen":"m","num":"p"},{"role":"present_2fp","form":"تَشْرَكْنَ","in_corpus":false,"count":null,"asp":"i","per":"2","gen":"f","num":"p"},{"role":"present_3ms","form":"يَشْرَك","in_corpus":true,"count":11,"asp":"i","per":"3","gen":"m","num":"s"},{"role":"present_3fs","form":"تَشْرَك","in_corpus":true,"count":8,"asp":"i","per":"3","gen":"f","num":"s"},{"role":"present_3md","form":"يَشْرَكانِ","in_corpus":false,"count":null,"asp":"i","per":"3","gen":"m","num":"d"},{"role":"present_3md","form":"يَشْرَكا","in_corpus":false,"count":null,"asp":"i","per":"3","gen":"m","num":"d"},{"role":"present_3fd","form":"تَشْرَكانِ","in_corpus":false,"count":null,"asp":"i","per":"3","gen":"f","num":"d"},{"role":"present_3fd","form":"تَشْرَكا","in_corpus":false,"count":null,"asp":"i","per":"3","gen":"f","num":"d"},{"role":"present_3mp","form":"يَشْرَكُونَ","in_corpus":true,"count":10,"asp":"i","per":"3","gen":"m","num":"p"},{"role":"present_3mp","form":"يَشْرَكُوا","in_corpus":false,"count":null,"asp":"i","per":"3","gen":"m","num":"p"},{"role":"present_3fp","form":"يَشْرَكْنَ","in_corpus":false,"count":null,"asp":"i","per":"3","gen":"f","num":"p"},{"role":"present_1ms","form":"أَشْرَك","in_corpus":true,"count":17,"asp":"i","per":"1","gen":"m","num":"s"},{"role":"present_1mp","form":"نَشْرَك","in_corpus":true,"count":1,"asp":"i","per":"1","gen":"m","num":"p"},{"role":"past_1mp","form":"شَرِكْنا","in_corpus":false,"count":null,"asp":"p","per":"1","gen":"m","num":"p"},{"role":"past_1ms","form":"شَرِكْتُ","in_corpus":false,"count":null,"asp":"p","per":"1","gen":"m","num":"s"}],"frequency_in_corpus":74,"cross_references":{"qac":{"found":true,"lemma_key":"شَرِكَ","root":"شرك","pos":"N","occurrence_count":5},"wiktextract":{"found":true,"entry_count":5,"pos_tags":["adj","noun","verb"],"has_etymology":true,"sense_count":10},"lanes":{"found":true,"entry_ids":["","n22220","n22221","n22222","n22223"],"search_url":"https://lanelexicon.com/?s=%D8%B4%D9%8E%D8%B1%D9%90%D9%83%D9%8E"}},"translations":null,"definition":{"source":"wiktextract","senses":[{"pos":"verb","gloss":"to have the shoe strings broken","tags":["obsolete"]},{"pos":"verb","gloss":"to share, to participate with (someone)","tags":["transitive"]},{"pos":"verb","gloss":"to become a partner, to be a participant, to be an associate"},{"pos":"noun","gloss":"verbal noun of شَرِكَ (šarika) (form I)","tags":["form-of","noun-from-verb"]},{"pos":"noun","gloss":"polytheism, idolatry","tags":["uncountable"],"examples":[{"text":"وَإِذْ قَالَ لُقْمَانُ لِٱبْنِهِ وَهُوَ يَعِظُهُ يَا بُنَيَّ لَا تُشْرِكْ بِٱللّٰهِۖ إِنَّ ٱلشِّرْكَ لَظُلْمٌ عَظِيمٌ","english":"When Luqman said to his son, as he advised him: \"O my son! Do not ascribe any partners to God. Polytheism is indeed a great injustice.\""},{"text":"إِن تَدْعُوهُمْ لَا يَسْمَعُوا دُعَاءَكُمْ وَلَوْ سَمِعُوا مَا ٱسْتَجَابُوا لَكُمْۖ وَيَوْمَ ٱلْقِيَامَةِ يَكْفُرُونَ بِشِرْكِكُمْۚ وَلَا يُنَبِّئُكَ مِثْلُ خَبِيرٍ","english":"If you invoke them they will not hear your invocation, and even if they heard they cannot respond to you, and on the Day of Resurrection they will forswear your polytheism, and none can inform you like the One who is all-aware."}]},{"pos":"noun","gloss":"share","tags":["countable"]},{"pos":"noun","gloss":"net, snare, trap, booby trap"},{"pos":"noun","gloss":"plural of شِرَاك (širāk, “shoelace”)","tags":["form-of","plural"]},{"pos":"noun","gloss":"plural of شَرَك (šarak, “net, snare”)","tags":["form-of","plural"]},{"pos":"adj","gloss":"spurious, unsound, phony, false"}]},"etymology":{"source":"wiktextract","text":"The meaning of associating partners to a god or sharing allegiance across multiple gods is, according to Jeffery 1938, a semantic loan from Old South Arabian 𐩦𐩧𐩫 (s²rk).\n\nSee the etymology of the corresponding lemma form."},"ipa":null,"lanes_definition":{"source":"lanes","entries":[{"entry_id":"n22220","headword_ar":"شَرْكٌ","root":"$rk","body":[{"kind":"text","text":": see what next follows."}],"source_refs":[]},{"entry_id":"n22221","headword_ar":"شِرْكٌ","root":"$rk","body":[{"kind":"text","text":"is an inf. n. of"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"$arikahu","text_ar":"شَرِكَهُ"},{"kind":"text","text":", as mentioned in the"},{"kind":"page_break","n":1542},{"kind":"text","text":"first sentence of this art.: (Mgh, Msb:) or a subst. therefrom: (S:) and is"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"syn. with"},{"kind":"text","text":"↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"$irokapN","text_ar":"شِرْكَةٌ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":", [signifying"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"A sharing, participating"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"participation, partaking,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"copartnership,"},{"kind":"text","text":"and mentioned before as an inf. n.,] (K,) as also are ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"$arikN","text_ar":"شَرِكٌ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":"and ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"$arikapN","text_ar":"شَرِكَةٌ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":", [likewise mentioned before as inf. ns.,] and ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"$arokN","text_ar":"شَرْكٌ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":"and ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"$arokapN","text_ar":"شَرْكَةٌ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":", (MF, TA,) and so is ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"$urokapN","text_ar":"شُرْكَةٌ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":", with damm, (K,) this last said by MF to be unknown, but it is common in Syria, almost to the exclusion of the other dial. vars. mentioned above. (TA.) An ex. of the first occurs in a trad, of Mo'ádh,"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A^ajaAza bayona A^aholi Alyamani","text_ar":"اَجَازَ بَيْنَ اَهْلِ اليَمَنِ"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Al$~iroka","text_ar":"الشِّرْكَ"},{"kind":"text","text":", meaning ["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He allowed, among the people of El-Yemen,"},{"kind":"text","text":"]"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"the sharing, one with another,"},{"kind":"text","text":"("},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"AlAi$otiraAk","text_ar":"الاِشْتِرَاك"},{"kind":"text","text":",)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"in land"},{"kind":"text","text":"[and app."},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"its produce"},{"kind":"text","text":"],"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"by its owner giving it to another for the half"},{"kind":"text","text":"[app."},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"of its produce"},{"kind":"text","text":"], or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"the third,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"the like thereof:"},{"kind":"text","text":"and a similar ex. of the same word occurs in another trad. (TA.) See also an ex. in a verse cited above, conj. 3. And one says,"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"ragibonaA fiY $irokikumo","text_ar":"رَغِبْنَا فِى شِرْكِكُمْ"},{"kind":"text","text":", meaning"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"We are desirous of sharing with you in affinity,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"relationship by marriage."},{"kind":"text","text":"(K, * TA.) ―         -b2-  And"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"A share:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(Mgh, O, Msb, TA:) as in the saying,"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"biyEa $irokN mino daArihi","text_ar":"بِيعَ شِرْكٌ مِنْ دَارِهِ"},{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"A share of his house was sold"},{"kind":"text","text":"]: (Mgh:) and as in the saying,"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A^aEotaqa","text_ar":"اَعْتَقَ"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"$irokFA lahu fiY EabodK","text_ar":"شِرْكًا لَهُ فِى عَبْدٍ"},{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He emancipated a share belonging to him in a slave"},{"kind":"text","text":"]: (Msb:) pl."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A^a$oraAkN","text_ar":"اَشْرَاكٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":". (O, Msb, TA.) [See a verse of Lebeed cited voce"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"zaEaAmapN","text_ar":"زَعَامَةٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":".] ―         -b3-  It is also a subst. from"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A^a$oraka biA@ll~`hi","text_ar":"اَشْرَكَ بِا@للّٰهِ"},{"kind":"text","text":"; (Mgh, Msb, K, TA;) thus in the Kur xxxi. 12; (Mgh, TA;) meaning The"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"attribution of a"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"$ariyk","text_ar":"شَرِيك"},{"kind":"text","text":"[or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"copartner"},{"kind":"text","text":"&c., or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"of"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"$urakaA='","text_ar":"شُرَكَا=ء"},{"kind":"text","text":"i. e."},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"copartners"},{"kind":"text","text":"&c., (see 4,)]"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"to God:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(Mgh:) [so that it may be rendered"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"belief in a plurality of gods:"},{"kind":"text","text":"] and [in a wider sense,]"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"unbelief"},{"kind":"text","text":"[or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"misbelief"},{"kind":"text","text":"]; syn."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"kuforN","text_ar":"كُفْرٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":". (S, Msb, K, TA.) And it is also expl. as meaning"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"Hypocrisy:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(Mgh, TA:) so in the saying of the Prophet,"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A_in~a A^axowafa maA A^axaAfu EalaY A^um~atiY Al$~iroku","text_ar":"اـِنَّ اَخْوَفَ مَا اَخَافُ عَلَى اُمَّتِى الشِّرْكُ"},{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"Verily the most fearful of what I fear for my people is hypocrisy"},{"kind":"text","text":"]: (Mgh:) and so in the trad.,"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Al$~iroku A^axofaY fiY A^um~atiY mino dabiybi Aln~amoli","text_ar":"الشِّرْكُ اَخْفَى فِى اُمَّتِى مِنْ دَبِيبِ النَّمْلِ"},{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"Hypocrisy is more latent in my people than the creeping of ants"},{"kind":"text","text":"]. (IAth, TA.) ―         -b4-  See also"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"$ariykN","text_ar":"شَرِيكٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":", in two places."}],"source_refs":["Mgh","Msb","S","K","MF","TA","O"]},{"entry_id":"n22222","headword_ar":"شَرَكٌ","root":"$rk","body":[{"kind":"text","text":"The"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"HibaAlap","text_ar":"حِبَالَة"},{"kind":"text","text":"[properly a sing., meaning"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"snare,"},{"kind":"text","text":"but here app. used as a gen. n., meaning"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"snares,"},{"kind":"text","text":"as will be seen from what follows,]"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"of the"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"SaAy^id","text_ar":"صَايِد"},{"kind":"text","text":"[i. e."},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"sportsman,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"catcher of game,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"wild animals,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"birds"},{"kind":"text","text":"]; one of which is called ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"$arakapN","text_ar":"شَرَكَةٌ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":": (S, O:) the meaning of the"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"$arak","text_ar":"شَرَك"},{"kind":"text","text":"of the"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"SaAy^id","text_ar":"صَايِد"},{"kind":"text","text":"is well known; and the pl. is"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A^a$oraAkN","text_ar":"اَشْرَاكٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"; like"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"sababN","text_ar":"سَبَبٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A^asobaAbN","text_ar":"اَسْبَابٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":": or, as some say,"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"$arakN","text_ar":"شَرَكٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"is the pl. of ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"$arakapN","text_ar":"شَرَكَةٌ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":", [or rather is a coll. gen. n. of which ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"$arakapN","text_ar":"شَرَكَةٌ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":"is the n. un.,] like"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"qaSabN","text_ar":"قَصَبٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"qaSabapN","text_ar":"قَصَبَةٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":": (Msb:) [i. e.,]"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"$arakN","text_ar":"شَرَكٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"signifies the"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"HabaAy^il","text_ar":"حَبَايِل"},{"kind":"text","text":"[or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"snares,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or by this may perhaps be meant the"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"cords composing a snare,"},{"kind":"text","text":"for"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"HabaAy^ilu","text_ar":"حَبَايِلُ"},{"kind":"text","text":"is an anomalous pl. of"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"HabolN","text_ar":"حَبْلٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":",]"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"for catching wild animals"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"the like;"},{"kind":"text","text":"and"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"what is,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"are, set up for"},{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"catching"},{"kind":"text","text":"]"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"birds:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(K, TA:) one whereof is said to be called ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"$arakapN","text_ar":"شَرَكَةٌ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":"[a term used in the K, in art."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"$bk","text_ar":"شبك"},{"kind":"text","text":", as the explanation of"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"$abakapN","text_ar":"شَبَكَةٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":", which means"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"a net"},{"kind":"text","text":"]: (TA:) and the pl. of"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"$arakN","text_ar":"شَرَكٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"is"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"$urukN","text_ar":"شُرُكٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":", with two dammehs, which is extr. [with respect to analogy, like"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"fulukN","text_ar":"فُلُكٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"pl. of"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"falakN","text_ar":"فَلَكٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"]. (K.) Hence the trad.,"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A^aEuw*u bika mino $ar~i","text_ar":"اَعُوذُ بِكَ مِنْ شَرِّ"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Al$~ayoTaAni wa$arakihi","text_ar":"الشَّيْطَانِ وَشَرَكِهِ"},{"kind":"text","text":", meaning"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"HabaAy^ilihi wamaSaAyidihi","text_ar":"حَبَايِلِهِ وَمَصَايِدِهِ"},{"kind":"text","text":"[i. e."},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"I seek protection by Thee from the mischief of the Devil, and his snares"},{"kind":"text","text":"]. (TA.) ―         -b2-"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"$araku AlT~ariyqi","text_ar":"شَرَكُ الطَّرِيقِ"},{"kind":"text","text":"means"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"The main and middle parts of the road;"},{"kind":"text","text":"(S, K;) syn."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"jawaAd~uhu","text_ar":"جَوَادُّهُ"},{"kind":"text","text":": or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"the tracks that are"},{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"conspicuous and distinct,"},{"kind":"text","text":"]"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"not obscure to one nor blended together:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(K:) pl. [or rather coll. gen. n.] of ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"$arakapN","text_ar":"شَرَكَةٌ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":": (S:) or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"the"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A^anosaAE","text_ar":"اَنْسَاع"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"of the road;"},{"kind":"text","text":"(As, TA;) i. e."},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"the furrows of the road, made by the beasts with their legs"},{"kind":"text","text":"[or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"feet"},{"kind":"text","text":"]"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"in its surface, a"},{"kind":"text","text":"↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"$arakap","text_ar":"شَرَكَة","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"here and another by the side of it:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(TA:) or"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A^a$oraAkN","text_ar":"اَشْرَاكٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"[is its pl., and] signifies the"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"small tracks that branch off"},{"kind":"text","text":"from the main road"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"and then stop,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"terminate."},{"kind":"text","text":"(Sh, TA.) [See"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A^us~N","text_ar":"اُسٌّ"},{"kind":"text","text":".]"}],"source_refs":["S","O","Msb","K","TA"]},{"entry_id":"n22223","headword_ar":"شَرِكٌ","root":"$rk","body":[{"kind":"text","text":": see"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"$irokN","text_ar":"شِرْكٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":", first sentence."}],"source_refs":[]}]}}